definition: Mother(x, y) ∧ Mother(z, x) → Grandmother(z, y)
Mother(z, x) ∧ Child(y, z) ∧ (x ≠ y) → Sibling(x, y)
Mother(x, y) ∧ Mother(z, x) ∧ Daughter(w, z) → Aunt(w, y)
SisterOf(x, y) → BrotherOf(y, x) [if y is Male]
Mother(a, b) ∧ Grandmother(c, a) ∧ Daughter(d, c) → FirstCousinOnceRemoved(d, b)
Father(a, b) ∧ FirstCousin(c, a) ∧ Grandchild(d, c) → FirstCousinOnceRemoved(d, b)
